{"tid":775150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓籍女子被情困 坪洲吊頸亡","createTime":"2018-08-11T02:11:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T04:37:02.000Z","uid":41404,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6a73d07ea6575e8e55a46eeff2f438dd867fc6ee","tid":775150,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T02:11:25.000Z","msg":"凌晨3時36分，坪洲坪利路18號一單位，一名41歲韓籍女子在梯間以電線上吊，保安發現報警。消防員到場將女事主解下，證實已經死亡。<br />\n<br />\n死者持護照，警方於現場撿獲遺書，據了解，女事主最近與男友分手，受感情問題困擾；警方初步調查相信事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180811/58549775\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180811%2F58549775&d=QBSkKEYAiAUBAIaFAeT1IG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=c05ef794\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180811%2F58549775&h=a1c84ad0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180811/58549775</a>"},{"pid":"a994c6d59e21c864a77f379456cd83afda32bde5","tid":775150,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T02:13:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/maps/@22.2872786,114.0367459,3a,75y,109.17h,99.67t/data=!3m7!1e1!3m5!1sw-3SUPuzYzTbsPM-AroDKw!2e0!6s%2F%2Fgeo0.ggpht.com%2Fcbk%3Fpanoid%3Dw-3SUPuzYzTbsPM-AroDKw%26output%3Dthumbnail%26cb_client%3Dmaps_sv.tactile.gps%26thumb%3D2%26w%3D203%26h%3D100%26yaw%3D115.591415%26pitch%3D0%26thumbfov%3D100!7i13312!8i6656?hl=zh-TW&amp;authuser=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Fmaps%2F%4022.2872786%2C114.0367459%2C3a%2C75y%2C109.17h%2C99.67t%2Fdata%3D%213m7%211e1%213m5%211sw-3SUPuzYz